• Advertising ID (e.g., Google Advertising ID, IDFA)
• IP address
• Location data (if enabled)
• Information about your use of the app and advertisements
Purpose of Processing:
The data is processed to:
• Provide relevant advertisements
• Measure the performance of advertising campaigns
• Prevent fraud and abuse
This is carried out on the basis of your consent according to Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR.
Data Sharing:
AppLovin may share the collected data with its partners and service providers to fulfill the purposes mentioned above.
Data Transfer to Third Countries:
Your data may be transferred to countries outside the European Economic Area (EEA), in particular the USA. We ensure that appropriate data protection measures, such as Standard Contractual Clauses, are taken to ensure an adequate level of data protection.
Right to Object and Removal Options ("Opt-Out"):
You can withdraw your consent to AppLovin’s data processing at any time with future effect:
• In the app: Adjust your preferences in the privacy settings of our app.
• Device settings: Reset the advertising ID in your device settings or disable personalized advertising.
For more information on data processing by AppLovin and its partner networks, please refer to the
AppLovin Privacy Policy
and the respective third-party providers.
