https://www.linkedin.com/legal/privacy-policy
. If you are logged into LinkedIn, you can deactivate data collection at any time by clicking on the following link:
https://www.linkedin.com/psettings/enhanced-advertising.
13.4 Legal basis
The legal basis for using Hubspot services is Article 6 I f DS-GDPR – legitimate interest. Our legitimate interest in using this service is to optimise our marketing measures and improve the service quality on our website.
